author: aconway
msg: DISPATCH-56: Unifiy C and python management agents.
There are 2 management agents.
Previously the C agent was at the default address $management, python agent at $management2
This commit completes all missing features of the python agent and makes it the default on $management.
The old C agent is still available on $cmanagement, but it is deprecated and will be removed.
- Added C entity types to the python schema: router.link, router.address, router.node, connection, allocator
- Update attribute values from C in python agent.
- Implemented get-operations, get-attributes, get-mgmt-nodes
- Added optional file:line in logging.

author: stefan2
msg: Finalize work on svn_fs_fs__get_stats API.  Add cancellation support
to the API and make svnfsfs actually provide a standard cancellation
callback.
* subversion/svnfsfs/svnfsfs.h
(check_cancel): Declare global cancellation callback to be accessible
to all sub-commands.
* subversion/svnfsfs/svnfsfs.c
(check_cancel): New global cancellation callback. Copied over from
svnadmin.c
* subversion/svnfsfs/stats-cmd.c
(query_t): Tweak docstrings and add cancellation callback members.
(read_phys_pack_file,
read_phys_revision_file,
read_log_rev_or_packfile): Invoke the cancellation callback once
in a while.
(create_query): Store cancellation callbacks in the query struct.
(svn_fs_fs__get_stats): Add cancellation support.
(subcommand__stats): Update API caller.
